### 需求API测试

### 变量设置
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081/api
@authToken = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 用户登录获取Token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 获取所有需求
GET {{baseUrl}}/requirements
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 获取单个需求
GET {{baseUrl}}/requirements/b8f4c5a2-035c-480d-9e7a-e8fcdeba965b
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 创建新需求
POST {{baseUrl}}/requirements
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "测试需求标题",
  "description": "这是一个用于测试的需求描述，包含详细的需求内容。"
}

### 更新需求
PUT {{baseUrl}}/requirements/b8f4c5a2-035c-480d-9e7a-e8fcdeba965b
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "更新后的需求标题",
  "description": "这是更新后的需求描述内容。",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### 删除需求
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/requirements/b8f4c5a2-035c-480d-9e7a-e8fcdeba965b
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}